show.description: Power, politics aur pyaar ke dangerous games mein kaun jeetega? Black Widow ki kahani hai ek aise mutant ki jo apne past se ladte hue duniya ko nayi direction de rahi hai. To ready ho jaiye, ye life-changing game dekhne aur janane ke liye Black Widow Ka Sach!
